Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果入水有force act on 背包 <br />\n咁根據牛三定律<br />\n背包個force act on 水係向下喎<br />\n<br />\n不過 噴出嚟嘅水force 夠大<br />\n咁向上嘅force 就足夠抵消背包act on 水嘅向下force 再加上向上飛嘅力<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 讀開英文physics 唔知點釋中文<br />\n有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係net force 向上？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3ed8dce17b17c0706c358b2f5b008042250bc693","tid":103163,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XY2z57n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXY2z57n.jpg&h=2a87a8e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解唔係(A)水直接施力於背包，為上托力，而牛三定律(B)背包施返力於水，令水轉向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你嗰諗法大致正確<br />\n但你錯左一個concept<br />\n<br />\n作用力和反作用力<br />\n係同時產生(作用係對方)<br />\n<br />\nA,B其實係無先後次序<br />\n但要做LQ，<br />\n就答B再答A"},{"pid":"3e8ec86e743c61ad84a1e48634345e2f821ac8d3","tid":103163,"uid":13021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XY2z57n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXY2z57n.jpg&h=2a87a8e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解唔係(A)水直接施力於背包，為上托力，而牛三定律(B)背包施返力於水，令水轉向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你嗰諗法大致正確<br />\n但你錯左一個concept<br />\n<br />\n作用力和反作用力<br />\n係同時產生(作用係對方)<br />\n<br />\nA,B其實係無先後次序<br />\n但要做LQ，<br />\n就答B再答A</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打 不過我有講過作用力同反作用力唔係同時產生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacbf7296f7401c13b5bbce53136b47e68841ccc","tid":103163,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"你係唔係想問<br />\n點解marking要提<br />\n牛頓第二定律？"},{"pid":"3332d3d9388e5c35f3c65f80765efc63d4b28cad","tid":103163,"uid":57266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T23:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XY2z57n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXY2z57n.jpg&h=2a87a8e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解唔係(A)水直接施力於背包，為上托力，而牛三定律(B)背包施返力於水，令水轉向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你嗰諗法大致正確<br />\n但你錯左一個concept<br />\n<br />\n作用力和反作用力<br />\n係同時產生(作用係對方)<br />\n<br />\nA,B其實係無先後次序<br />\n但要做LQ，<br />\n就答B再答A</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你認為A同B有分別？"},{"pid":"775c5aaa03696968a5dce316a328fa7d950daaf2","tid":103163,"uid":27055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"marking scheme 答案係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33ca807076b1b96016bc8f813868069cf6d9064","tid":103163,"uid":41525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"水噴出泥會有向下既作用力<br />\n同向上既反作用力<br />\n反作用力大過人既重量<br />\n所以有上托力<br />\n<br />\n咁樣會唔會合理d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80efb2b2eaf4f0de7ae6e75be0913636a39da0c6","tid":103163,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"Marking答案？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477dfe18927e9b86013d9f29982c2b9ee5ca29f3","tid":103163,"uid":21025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"Consider Momentum and force relationship<br />\n<br />\nF=(m&bull;vi - m&bull;vf)/(delta) t<br />\n<br />\nF=m&bull;[(vi - vf)/delta t]<br />\n<br />\nTake upward as positive, then<br />\n<br />\nF=m&bull;[(vi - (-vf))/delta t]<br />\n<br />\nAs vi and vf in same magnitude but differs in direction,<br />\n<br />\nF=m&bull;[(2vi)/delta t], where 2vi=delta v<br />\n<br />\nF=m&bull;[(delta v)/(delta t)], where [(delta v)/(delta t)] is acceleration, positive quantity<br />\n<br />\nHence change in momentum of water stream can create a uplift force, which cancel out the weight of a person"},{"pid":"2919785f97197b23352397aeb6adf75fea1298e0","tid":103163,"uid":21025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"Welcome comments"}]}